**The Soft XP logo is designed to convey the program's focus on soft skills training for individuals seeking to enhance their career prospects. The logo appears in two versions, one against a black background for product branding, and the other against white on the website. The logo includes an icon that accompanies the Soft XP text, but the specific icon is open to suggestions. The branding for Soft XP includes a prism with 36 individual colors, each representing one of the 36 courses offered in the program. The prism is a visual representation of the variety of soft skills covered in the program. The tone of the Soft XP branding is professional and focused on the critical soft skills that are in high demand by top corporate hiring managers. Soft XP's self-guided and self-paced comprehensive program emphasizes the importance of developing soft skills to achieve success in any industry, and the courses cover a broad range of topics, including effective communication, teamwork, problem-solving, critical thinking, leadership, and time management. Whether you are a recent graduate, a seasoned professional, or an entrepreneur, Soft XP can help you acquire the skills you need to advance your career or business.** - <@1075074103553306714> (fast)
